{"tid":1899711,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[抗爭路上]文宣心血x抗爭歷程集結成書","createTime":"2020-02-26T18:52:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T17:54:45.000Z","uid":220550,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"660c37aab76c65fca40acbf5b2430a8d3b55bf8d","tid":1899711,"uid":220550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T18:52:59.000Z","msg":"啱啱見到Follow開嘅畫家宣傳呢本<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Umbrella Uplifting</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dtijb5G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdtijb5G.jpg&h=2feea0f9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vAaYsD2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvAaYsD2.jpg&h=cee4ff53&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BK92Ui2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBK92Ui2.jpg&h=3ebe7937&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SVccw5J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSVccw5J.jpg&h=f92f39aa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1YpN5qK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1YpN5qK.jpg&h=50f9dfcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係英國嘅手足將一路以嚟嘅文宣集結成書<br />\n以藝術嘅角度將今次嘅抗爭紀錄落嚟<br />\n唔單止份量夠誠意都好夠<br />\n因為！！！<br />\n佢哋嘅團隊花左幾個月時間email/message啲artists，仲有同telegram同文宣group admin傾<br />\n作品都<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有經作者同意</span></span>先放落本書度！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且本書係非牟利嘅<br />\n佢哋話因為星火執咗，扣除成本後嘅收益主要會喺外國整多啲書/exhibition向外國宣傳個示威，有多就會捐去HK FREE PRESS<br />\n咁有心整理文宣手足嘅作品一定要大大力支持啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢哋宜家係Kickstarter集緊資：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/umbrellauprising/umbrella-uprising-protest-arts-of-hong-kong-protests\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kickstarter.com%2Fprojects%2Fumbrellauprising%2Fumbrella-uprising-protest-arts-of-hong-kong-protests&d=dKvfM97HALqNkq2vb6iplJMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=f1a34d7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/umbrellauprising/umbrella-uprising-protest-arts-of-hong-kong-protests</a><br />\n<br />\n亦都可以去Facebook Follow佢哋：<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/UmbrellaUprising/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FUmbrellaUprising%2F&d=dKvfM97HALqNkq2vb6iplJMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=d138b6e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/UmbrellaUprising/</a><br />\n<br />\n大家一齊支持集資啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為我好想收藏本書實物啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></strong>"},{"pid":"fff4afd87b3141bf99e65f2473008b9705a39426","tid":1899711,"uid":21008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T18:54:48.000Z","msg":"Push!!!!"},{"pid":"9224c31ec383c8167c44f5ff046f03be118c1ab3","tid":1899711,"uid":220550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T19:06:03.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34adcd7b3f29ed9214bbc6d0fe1a422d4f280712","tid":1899711,"uid":220550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T19:20:52.000Z","msg":"831<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ccap7PU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fccap7PU.jpg&h=be55ffbb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"62144514155bf2a17b34b31fd4041bf18a6f074e","tid":1899711,"uid":220550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T02:11:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ac890782959dee4a859415678200edd4ad